title: Ep - 28 - Dorinda Medley of Real Housewives of New York
description:
Dorinda Medley discusses the new season of Real Housewives of New York and her life before Bravo, Paul Zahn and Kate cover Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and Atlanta, and Dana Bowling helps Kate cover this week’s episode of Bachelor and the premiere of Mama June: From Not to Hot on WE Tv.
